            "heading": "2019",
            "heading_size": "h5",
            "content": "<p>When we did the finishing touches of our newest model, the Legacy, we chose the most eco-conscious vegan leather and also covered the front and back of the unit with hemp textile, which we think is a statement for all the legality issues that were in place for centuries around hemp. ;)</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "button",
