            "video_autoplay": true,
            "heading": "2020",
            "heading_size": "h5",
            "content": "<p>We started shipping most of our orders under 16 oz, in plant-based bubble wrap envelopes (yes, full fledged food for microorganisms when thrown away), and we are damn proud about that! :)</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "button",
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
